Class dasg_i_SearchAdversarialIterativeDeepeningAlphaBeta<STATE,ACTION,PLAYER>

  • java.lang.Object
    • reuze.dasg_i_SearchAdversarialIterativeDeepeningAlphaBeta<STATE,ACTION,PLAYER>

    All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class dasg_i_SearchAdversarialIterativeDeepeningAlphaBeta<STATE,ACTION,PLAYER>
extends java.lang.Object
implements dasg_i_SearchAdversarial<STATE,ACTION>
    Implements an iterative deepening Minimax search with alpha-beta pruning and action ordering. Maximal computation time is specified in seconds. The algorithm is implemented as template method and can be configured and tuned by subclassing.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
